<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"
      th:replace="layout :: layout(~{::title}, ~{::main})">
<head>
    <title>Tamper-Proof Academic Certificates</title>
</head>
<body>
<main>
    <section class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                Tamper-Proof Academic Certificates
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">
                Issue, digitally sign, and verify academic certificates using RSA-2048 and SHA-256 — all in one secure portal.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a th:href="@{/verify}"
               class="block rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
                <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Verify a Certificate</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                    Enter a certificate ID to confirm authenticity instantly.
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700">Go to Verify →</div>
            </a>

            <a th:href="@{/login}"
               class="block rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
                <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Admin Portal</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                    Generate keys, issue certificates, and manage records.
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700">Go to Login →</div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How it works</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700">Step 1</div>
                <div class="mt-2 font-semibold">Issue</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Admin records the student and award details.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700">Step 2</div>
                <div class="mt-2 font-semibold">Sign</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">System hashes the data and signs the hash with RSA.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700">Step 3</div>
                <div class="mt-2 font-semibold">Verify</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Anyone can verify the signature using the stored public key.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>

